room_title: Escape room "Villain’s Lair" by Unchained STL in St. Louis
room_address: 221 Spencer Road Suite I Saint Peters, MO 63376
room_description:
60 minutes until your work week is done! Just one more inspection, one more report to write and then your weekend starts. You can already taste the BBQ waiting for you at home. Just one more routine inspection… turns into anything but routine.
Who has turned this abandoned part of the tunnel system into their home and what are they doing with the blueprints for the water sanitation units in major cities across the country? Find out if your team has what it takes to stop the unknown villain and save the world!
